============================================
===================README===================
============================================

==============
===FEATURES===
==============

- A cube is moving above the tower.
- The player can press the Spacebar to bring down the cube.
- The cube is cut relatively to the tower.
- If the cube falls next to the tower's last cube, 
    then the game is over and the tower starts rotating.
- Else, the visible face of the tower is changed by a fluid animation.
- The score is displayed at the top of the screen.

- The player can press the spacebar again when he lost, to reset the game through an animation.